<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Developer Tool Suite</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    body { align-items: flex-start; padding-top: 80px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container" style="max-width: 1000px; gap: 40px;">

    <header>
      <h1>Dev<span>Toolkit</span></h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Multi-purpose tools for developers. Fast, private, and local.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="dashboard">
      
      <a href="/php-protector" class="tool-card">
        <span class="tag">Security</span>
        <div class="icon">🛡️</div>
        <h2>PHP Protector</h2>
        <p>Obfuscate PHP projects recursively. Preserve directory structure and encrypt source code with eval/base64.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/image-resizer" class="tool-card">
        <span class="tag">Images</span>
        <div class="icon">📐</div>
        <h2>Image Resizer</h2>
        <p>Professional image resizing with support for Cover, Contain, and Inside fitting. Recursive folder processing.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/image-converter" class="tool-card">
        <span class="tag">Optimization</span>
        <div class="icon">🔄</div>
        <h2>Image Converter</h2>
        <p>Convert and compress images to WebP, JPEG, PNG, or AVIF recursively. Dramatically reduce project asset sizes.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/pdf-compressor" class="tool-card">
        <span class="tag">Performance</span>
        <div class="icon">📄</div>
        <h2>PDF Compressor</h2>
        <p>Shrink large PDF folders with Ghostscript. Multiple quality levels with perfect structure preservation.</p>
      </a>

    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
